https://www.udemy.com/course/salesforce-development/learn/lecture/22873953#overview

1,process start
2,System validation rules
3,record triggered flows
4,before trigger
5,custom validation rules
6,duplicate rules
7,Save the record[not commit]
8,after trigger
9,assignment rules
10,auto response rules 
11,workflow rules
12,processes and flows
13,Escalation and entitlement rules
14,record triggered flows
15,roll up summary
16,sharing rule evaluation
17,commit all DML changes
18,post commit operations




